{
  "stem": "3605.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were tomatoes and carrots and [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] other vegetables [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that-- that you could make a-- a vegetable soup.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had also a self-help kitchen that we used to take over some food to-- to our friends and that are specifically in dire need.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some of the people, they, due to sickness, their parents passed away, and they were sick themselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a very rough situation in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It is nothing that people can here compare it with.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was worse than any jail you can imagine because you was just locked in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You couldn't go, and you [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] couldn't be your own master.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you did not have any source of food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Here, in a jail, you get three meals a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But this was not the situation over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, our group, got the news, because now and then, we got a contact person that smuggled into the ghetto-- in fact, her name was Minka Liebeskind, and she was the sister of our leader in Krakow, and his name was Dolek Liebeskind.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Libeskind.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "L-I-B-E-S-K-I-N-D.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Liebeskind.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was the leader of our organization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and we also had a-- a newsletter that they were making there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Gusta Davidson Draenger and Shimshon Shoemaker Draenger were writing the paper.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was called This was 'The Fighting Chalutz.' And they were also-- The Fighting Chalutz is the fighting pioneer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were also-- let's see, in 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so they were reaching out to other Zionist movements, and they joined them together to have both a spiritual and an armed resistance.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
